sub_title: Chief Operations Officer at Shimano EMEA | Driving growth through Supply Chain Management | Digital transformation | Leisure | Outdoor
summary:
Growing businesses by driving strategy to execution, with a long as well as short-term performance impact. “Always connecting the dots & the people”.

Natural leadership skills to take predominantly technical-oriented organizations into external orientation and positioning. Strong decisive nature helps to quickly build trust and cultivate a culture of accountability in these often operational and results-oriented environments. 

By harnessing a diversity of talents and resources, build a shared vision and swiftly gain buy-in, inspiring team members to be their best. With this organizational alignment, coaching teams to new levels of improved performance. 

Engineer organizational strategies and initiatives in response to emerging industry and marketplace trends. Skilled in analyzing and clarifying issues, advocating solutions, mobilizing cross-functional cooperation in complex organizations, and identifying strategic priorities.
